  <main>
    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/part-i/article-ii/section-201"
             temporalId="sSection 201">
      <num>Section 201</num>
      <heading>Procedural Authority</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The city shall have the power and may act pursuant to any procedure established by
               any law of the state, unless a different procedure is established by this Charter
               or by ordinance.</p>
      </content>
    </section>
  </main>
